Optimum Says Transnet to Close Richard Bay Line For 20-Days of Maintenance

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-14T11:21:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/optimum-says-transnet-to-close-richard-bay-line-for-20-days-of-maintenance.html
Optimum Coal Holdings (OPT)  Ltd. said the
freight rail unit of Transnet Ltd. plans to close its line to
the Richards Bay Coal Terminal from May 23 until June 11 for
maintenance.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  